akt
------------------------------------------
Ancestry and Kinship Tools

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libgomp1-14.4.0-1
  libhts3-1.23.1-1bl1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libhts-devel-1.23.1-1bl1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/Illumina/akt

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/Illumina/akt/archive/refs/tags/v0.3.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack akt-0.3.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./akt-0.3.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/akt-0.3.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/akt-0.3.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(akt)
  /usr/bin/akt.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/akt.README
  /usr/share/doc/akt/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/akt/README.md

